[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta9[/b]

[list]
[*]Added flashlight, muzzle flash, projectile, and explosion compatibility for Customizable Weaponry 2.0 and TFA Base weapons.
[*]Improved ARC9 flashlight placement so beams and lens flares follow the active attachment.
[*]Fixed duplicate ARC9 flashlight beams and flashlight key conflicts.
[*]Improved settings profile saving and sharing with smaller files and compact profile codes.
[*]Existing profile JSON can still be imported, viewed, and copied.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta8[/b]

[list]
[*]Added server-wide flashlight settings.
[*]Added a personal option to disable Better Lights.
[*]Added a muzzle flash blacklist.
[*]Improved the server and personal settings menus.
[*]Improved flashlight lens flare placement and color.
[*]Fixed gunfire lights appearing for some non-gun weapons.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta7[/b]

[list]
[*]Added advanced flashlight shadow settings.
[*]Improved flashlight shadow stability near props.
[*]Fixed scanner searchlights on some models.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta6[/b]

[list]
[*]Added flashlight lens flare settings.
[*]Fixed the player flashlight freezing with some camera addons.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta5[/b]

[list]
[*]Fixed the ARC9 flashlight setting.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta4[/b]

[list]
[*]Added integration settings for MW Base, ArcCW, and ARC9.
[*]Added M9K flashlight compatibility.
[*]Fixed flashlight battery HUD compatibility with Oxygen and Stamina.
[*]Fixed unwanted muzzle flashes on some NPC and NextBot attacks.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta3[/b]

[list]
[*]Added ArcCW flashlight and muzzle flash compatibility.
[*]Fixed Better Lights flashlight sounds for nearby players.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta2[/b]

[list]
[*]Improved MW Base muzzle flash handling.
[*]Better Lights flashlight can now attach to MW Base weapons. 
[*]Fixed eye glow appearing on some custom Combine NPC models.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.6.0-beta1[/b]

[list]
[*]This beta includes many under the hood changes, so some instability is possible.
[*]Fixed profile resets not restoring every personal setting.
[*]Fixed profile actions causing console errors for some players.
[*]Moved settings profiles into their own Profiles category.
[*]Added settings profiles for saving, loading, importing, and exporting personal settings.
[*]Added a personal settings reset option to the Profiles page.
[*]Added impact lights for Stun Stick hits.
[*]Added optional eye lights for Dog.
[*]Improved explosion flashes and reduced false flashes from removed entities.
[*]Improved scanner searchlights so they aim more reliably and shine farther.
[*]Improved muzzle flash placement for weapons with real muzzle attachments.
[*]Improved ARC9 muzzle flash handling.
[*]Improved held and dropped weapon light placement.
[*]Improved flashlight weapon attachment handling.
[*]Improved scanner lights, searchlights, and cleanup.
[*]Improved the settings menu layout and help text spacing.
[*]Improved flashlight and spotlight update handling.
[*]Cleaned up addon loading and networking internals.
[*]Cleaned up Antlion Worker glow placement.
[*]Fixed shotgun muzzle flashes creating extra lights per shot.
[*]Fixed unsupported weapons showing muzzle flashes from the player position.
[*]Fixed the Combine Mine idle glow toggle.
[*]Fixed scanner searchlight settings when changed after loading.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.5.2[/b]

[list]
[*]Added blue lights for Hunters, flechettes, and flechette blasts.
[*]Added blue muzzle flash and bullet impact lights for Striders.
[*]Added Hunter Chopper muzzle flash, bullet impact lights, and a spotlight.
[*]Added a model lookup tool for checking attachments, bones, skins, bodygroups, and materials.
[*]Added squashed Antlion Grub glow and combined Antlion lighting settings into one menu.
[*]Improved Manhack and Antlion Guardian light placement.
[*]Improved settings menu compatibility with custom skins.
[*]Improved translations and localization checks.
[*]Updated the Workshop page text.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.5.1[/b]

[list]
[*]Added flashlight color and flicker strength settings.
[*]Added a simple slider for flashlight sway strength.
[*]Improved flashlight behavior in vehicles.
[*]Cleaned up the flashlight settings menu, labels, and button styling.
[*]Fixed reset all settings not restoring every Better Lights option.
[*]Fixed flashlight texture and recent texture choices not resetting properly.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.5.0[/b]

[list]
[*]Added menu translations for several popular Garry's Mod languages.
[*]Added contributor notes for translation fixes and improvements.
[*]Updated the Workshop page with translation support details.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.4.3[/b]

[list]
[*]Added lights for spawned and dropped weapon pickups.
[*]Added pickup lights for AR2 ammo and optional lights for other ammo pickups.
[*]Added a flashlight forward offset setting.
[*]Improved the settings menu with better grouping and color pickers.
[*]Added an in-game changelog browser.
[*]Improved the About page with author, license, and support links.
[*]Improved rollermine color settings for detected skins.
[*]Improved flashlight behavior when no weapon is equipped.
[*]Improved flashlight compatibility with vehicles and server settings.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.4.2[/b]

[list]
[*]Added more player flashlight visual options.
[*]Added custom flashlight texture selection with previews.
[*]Improved the flashlight settings layout.
[*]Fixed flashlight behavior when changing levels.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.4.1[/b]

[list]
[*]Simplified the Better Lights flashlight settings.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.4.0[/b]

[list]
[*]Added a new toggle to quickly enable or disable Better Lights.
[*]Added an option to reset all Better Lights settings.
[*]Made the Better Lights flashlight disabled by default for new users.
[*]Reworked the flashlight settings menu to separate personal and server options.
[*]Moved flashlight sound preference to a personal setting.
[*]Added a changelog button to the About menu.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.3.5[/b]

[list]
[*]Added an option to disable Better Lights flashlight sounds and use the vanilla flashlight sounds.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.3.4[/b]

[list]
[*]When the flashlight module is disabled, it no longer still intercepts player input.
[*]Added a Beam Length slider for the Better Lights player flashlight.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.3.3[/b]

[list]
[*]Fixed the Better Lights player flashlight disappearing when using suit zoom with HUD addons such as HoloHUD2.
[*]The flashlight now falls back to a stable eye-position origin while zooming instead of relying on the first-person viewmodel attachment.
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.3.2[/b]

[list]
[*]Improved player flashlight compatibility with addons and gamemodes. 
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.3.1[/b]

[list]
[*]Fixed the player flashlight sometimes turning on but not turning off
[*]Improved flashlight toggle handling so it behaves more like the vanilla flashlight
[*]Added protection against duplicate flashlight input events
[*]Prevented the vanilla flashlight from getting stuck on behind the Better Lights flashlight
[/list]

[b]Better Lights v1.3.0[/b]

[list]
[*]Added a new BetterLights player flashlight module
[*]Added a dedicated Flashlight settings category
[*]Custom sounds for the flashlight
[*]Code cleanup and slight performance improvements. 
